We've managed to get replicas of the one the guards wear for when they pick up the money.
我们弄到了警卫取钱时穿的制服复制品。

270
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,520
Got it.
明白了。

271
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,240
No problem, boss.
没问题，老大。

272
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:22,880
When you get inside, tell them that you're filling in for Carl and Tom, and say that
进去后，告诉他们你们是替卡尔和汤姆的班，就说他们今天走另一条路线。

273
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,680
they're on another route today.
另一条路线。

274
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,040
Don't lose your cool.
别失去冷静。

275
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:27,040
Just act natural.
自然点就行。

276
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:29,760
What if they want to call and confirm?
如果他们想打电话确认呢？

277
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,760
You let them.
让他们打。

278
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,760
What?
什么？

279
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:32,760
Don't worry.
别担心。

280
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:36,360
We have the phones tapped, so the call will be patched through to me, and I'll pretend
我们监听了电话，所以电话会转接到我这里，我会假装是运输公司。

281
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,360
to be the transport company.
运输公司。

282
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,360
You're so clever, boss.
老大，你真聪明。

283
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,360
Okay, shut up.
好了，闭嘴。

284
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:44,080
Only take as much money as you can fit in these bags.
只拿能装进这些袋子的钱。

285
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,080
Don't get greedy.
别贪心。

286
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,080
Are you ready?
准备好了吗？

287
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,080
Let's go.
走吧。

288
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:57,400
So there's a lot of movies about bank robberies, but obviously they happen in real life.
关于银行抢劫的电影很多，但显然现实中也会发生。

